snippet.title: Arcade Longplay - Fast Freddie (1982) Atari
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the arcade game Fast Freddie. Released back in 1982 by Kaneko under Atari license, the game is a clone of the game Fly-Boy. A side scrolling kick-em up.
